THE FIRMWARE ELECTRICAL ENGINEERING INTENDED TO RELEASE HAS BEEN IN USE BY MANUFACTURING SINCE THE INITIAL RELEASE OF 064541-5(WAS SUPPLIED BY THE PROJECT ENGINEER).
